WEBVTT

00:00:23.485 --> 00:00:24.553
froy Lipis,

00:00:24.553 --> 00:00:27.123
vos zet men dort oyf di fotografye?

00:00:27.197 --> 00:00:29.978
do UNK in dem kolkhoz,

00:00:29.978 --> 00:00:34.273
ven s'iz shoyn geven kalt in droysn, s'iz shoyn geven der ershter shney,

00:00:34.273 --> 00:00:38.432
hot men undz arayngetribn in ⟨Makikov⟩, vu s'iz yeder eyner oysgeshtorbn.

00:00:38.432 --> 00:00:40.196
do iz geven on,

00:00:40.196 --> 00:00:44.491
on pol, on gornisht. oyf tsement, oyf erd zenen mir gelign,

00:00:44.491 --> 00:00:47.509
oyf dr'erd. ⟨i⟩n yedn fentster azoyn⟨e⟩

00:00:47.509 --> 00:00:49.832
iz geven efsher tsu hundert mentshn.

00:00:49.832 --> 00:00:51.795
un geblibn iz fun zey,

00:00:52.003 --> 00:00:55.119
fun hundert iz mistome geblibn tsu tsen, fuftsn.

00:00:55.260 --> 00:00:59.349
ven, nokh der milkhome, ze'mir aheymgekumen, ze'mir geforn oyf keyver-oves,

00:00:59.349 --> 00:01:02.611
dortn vu di mentshn zenen mekaber geven.

00:01:02.618 --> 00:01:07.643
ho'mir SNIMAET ot di, do vu m'hot a mol fartribn mentshn,

00:01:07.643 --> 00:01:09.483
un tsu hundert mentshn,

00:01:09.483 --> 00:01:11.842
un azoy ⟨ot o⟩, eyns lebn dos andere,

00:01:11.842 --> 00:01:14.762
in shtroy hot men zikh gevalgert ayngeviklt,

00:01:14.835 --> 00:01:17.886
un, m'hot gelebt biz m'iz geshtorbn.

00:01:17.886 --> 00:01:21.967
UNK der KOROVNIK nokh geven, do vu m'hot gehaltn a mol,

00:01:22.159 --> 00:01:27.252
 shof, tsi ikh veys vos, UNK ze'mir, ho'mir SNIMAET, mir zol'mir vayzn

00:01:27.252 --> 00:01:29.920
yedn vi m'hot undz a mol fartribn.

00:01:29.942 --> 00:01:32.477
un demolts hot men gemakht di fotografye?

00:01:32.588 --> 00:01:34.407
gemakht,

00:01:34.407 --> 00:01:39.602
mayner a ⟨FREUND⟩ iz geforn mit mir, vos zayne eltern zenen oykh do geshtorbn.

00:01:39.602 --> 00:01:43.376
hot er gehat a FOTOAPPARAT, ze'mir geforn, un ze'mir gegan spetsyel,

00:01:43.376 --> 00:01:47.874
un mir ho'mir opgeSNIMAET, yeder, mir zol'mir op⟨UNK⟩kn vu

00:01:47.874 --> 00:01:52.431
undz ze'mir gelign, un vu di eltern zenen farfaln gevorn, un vu yeder,

00:01:52.888 --> 00:01:54.505
in dem, ⟨ot o⟩.

00:01:54.505 --> 00:01:55.481
un do,

00:01:55.555 --> 00:01:56.932
nisht ⟨get-⟩,

00:01:56.955 --> 00:02:00.276
a ayzerne hrubkele fle- iz geven,

00:02:00.276 --> 00:02:02.715
ober m'hot gehat mit vos tsu heytsn ⟨ober gornit⟩.

00:02:02.715 --> 00:02:06.204
in shtroy iz men gelign, eyns lebn s'andere, eyns lebn s'andere,

00:02:06.574 --> 00:02:07.912
in dem,

00:02:07.912 --> 00:02:09.131
kolkhoz.

00:02:14.860 --> 00:02:17.681
ver iz dortn oyf di foto⟨grafye⟩?

00:02:16.243 --> 00:02:17.902
dos bin ikh,

00:02:17.902 --> 00:02:20.670
far der milkhome, nokh in der heym,

00:02:20.670 --> 00:02:24.844
a tsvey yor biz di milkhome hot zikh ongehoybn, tsvey, dray yor,

00:02:25.153 --> 00:02:26.499
alts kind.

00:02:26.655 --> 00:02:29.704
un vi hot ir derhaltn di fotograf⟨ye⟩?

00:02:28.815 --> 00:02:34.867
di fotografye hob ikh ersht nokh der milkhome... bay undz in tsayt fun der milkhome iz ales farbrent gevorn.

00:02:34.941 --> 00:02:39.124
hot mayn eygener foter es mir geshikt.

00:02:39.784 --> 00:02:41.306
fun Argentine?

00:02:41.080 --> 00:02:45.045
fun Argentine, fun Buenos-Ayres. er hot dort, voynt dort.

00:02:45.437 --> 00:02:47.227
er hot mir geshikt es.

00:02:47.192 --> 00:02:48.193
a dank.

00:02:49.251 --> 00:02:50.568
un dos i-...

00:02:50.753 --> 00:02:53.749
ver iz ot do oyf yene fotograf⟨ye⟩?

00:02:52.590 --> 00:02:55.134
ot do iz mayn muter.

00:02:55.360 --> 00:02:57.249
dos iz mayn muter.

00:02:57.216 --> 00:02:58.070
yo.

00:02:57.249 --> 00:03:01.344
ikh hob zi nisht gekent un nisht gevust. zi iz geshtorbn...

00:02:59.888 --> 00:03:02.315
UNK in mitn UNK?

00:03:01.620 --> 00:03:06.086
yo., zi iz geshtorbn ven ikh bin geven alt a yor,

00:03:06.379 --> 00:03:10.025
un ikh hob nisht gevust biz nokh der milkhome.

00:03:10.025 --> 00:03:14.425
nokh der milkhome, i- in finef un fertsikstn, zeks un fertsikstn,

00:03:14.425 --> 00:03:19.644
iz ire a khaverte hot mir geshenkt dos bild ven m'hot mir shoyn dertseylt az dos iz mayn

00:03:19.644 --> 00:03:21.347
rikhtike mame.

00:03:21.853 --> 00:03:22.792
a dank.

00:03:40.753 --> 00:03:41.450
UNK

00:03:41.450 --> 00:03:42.182
⟨nu⟩?

00:03:42.424 --> 00:03:44.780
do bin ikh nokh der milkhome.

00:03:45.529 --> 00:03:48.071
bin alt fuftsn yor, zekhtsn.

00:03:50.406 --> 00:03:55.033
vet iberdreyen di fotografyes? ge- ongeshribn dortn epes?

00:03:54.709 --> 00:03:56.508
neyn, gornisht.

00:03:57.139 --> 00:03:59.372
dos bin ikh teykef...

00:04:00.244 --> 00:04:02.720
yor zekhtsn bin ikh alt do.

00:04:03.062 --> 00:04:03.900
a dank.

00:04:07.264 --> 00:04:09.738
di, dos bild,

00:04:09.846 --> 00:04:13.652
hob ikh geshikt dos kleyne bild ven kh'hob zikh dervust

00:04:13.652 --> 00:04:19.014
az kh'hob a foter, a, der eygener foter mayner, Gershn Bernshteyn,

00:04:19.014 --> 00:04:22.617
voynt in Buenos-Ayres, un er hot zikh gelozt tsu mir hern.

00:04:22.617 --> 00:04:27.661
hob ikh im geshikt mayn kleyn bild, un er hot mir krikgeshikt dos bild fun im.

00:04:27.661 --> 00:04:30.563
azoy az mayn foter iz er,

00:04:30.670 --> 00:04:32.537
Gershn Bernshteyn.

00:04:32.946 --> 00:04:35.898
un er hot gemakht fun dem bild

00:04:34.330 --> 00:04:36.505
fun dem kleynem bild

00:04:36.505 --> 00:04:38.542
ot dos groyse bild

00:04:36.535 --> 00:04:37.535
a ⟨bild⟩...?

00:04:38.685 --> 00:04:40.484
fun zikh mit mir.

00:04:41.301 --> 00:04:45.530
vi hot er zikh dervust az ir zent in NOWOSELITZA?

00:04:44.001 --> 00:04:50.492
er hot gefregt., er hot m- mentshn keyn Tshernovits geshribn, un er hot zikh derfregt tsu mir.

00:04:50.970 --> 00:04:52.685
er hot gevolt visn.

00:04:52.658 --> 00:04:53.529
a dank.

00:04:57.113 --> 00:04:59.059
dos iz, Basye.

00:04:59.059 --> 00:05:05.118
zi iz mir geven i a shvester, i a mame, un zi hot mir umedum un alemen geholfn.

00:05:05.837 --> 00:05:09.618
un dos iz di tsvey eyniklekh, hot zi geholfn mir khoven.

00:05:10.191 --> 00:05:12.902
dos zent ir mit Basye? ir zent ⟨dokh⟩...?

00:05:11.490 --> 00:05:15.516
ikh mit Basye. ikh bin oykh Basye un zi Basye.

00:05:15.507 --> 00:05:16.186
yo.

00:05:15.540 --> 00:05:23.155
un zi iz mir geven i a shvester, i a mame, ales. un hot mir geholfn khoven di eyniklekh oykh⟨et⟩.

00:05:23.208 --> 00:05:25.516
un di meydelekh zenen ay-...?

00:05:24.389 --> 00:05:28.579
⟨,⟩ fun der tokhter eyniklekh tsvey: Regine un Sabine.

00:05:28.635 --> 00:05:31.177
vu iz gemakht gevorn di fotogra⟨fye⟩?

00:05:30.087 --> 00:05:31.903
in Tshernovits.

00:05:34.035 --> 00:05:34.872
a dank.

00:05:39.334 --> 00:05:41.980
dos iz der bruder mayner, Moyshe.

00:05:41.980 --> 00:05:46.601
er iz in Erets-Yisroel geshtorbn krik mit tsvey yor. un dos iz zayn froy,

00:05:46.658 --> 00:05:47.884
Roz.

00:05:48.328 --> 00:05:51.511
iz oykh geven in lager. zi hot farloyrn dort

00:05:51.771 --> 00:05:54.026
dem foter un dos kind,

00:05:54.184 --> 00:05:55.275
ales.

00:05:56.597 --> 00:06:00.506
di shveger⟨in⟩ vos hot geboyrn dos kind UNK ⟨geshtorbn⟩?

00:05:59.027 --> 00:06:02.558
DA, zi hot geboyrn dos kind vos iz geshtorbn.

00:06:05.355 --> 00:06:06.255
a dank.

00:06:08.697 --> 00:06:11.987
dos iz di tokhter mayne zitst mit im.

00:06:08.726 --> 00:06:09.506
UNK

00:06:12.679 --> 00:06:17.212
zi iz, zi hot gev- zi iz geven oyf a bazukh ⟨in⟩ Erets-Yisroel?

00:06:15.514 --> 00:06:18.714
yo, zi iz geven in Erets-Yisroel, ⟨iz zi⟩ mit im.

00:06:19.648 --> 00:06:23.636
ir zent shoyn oykhet geven in Erets-Yisroel bazukhn di mishpokhe?

00:06:21.519 --> 00:06:22.194
yo.

00:06:24.812 --> 00:06:27.584
itster iz er shoyn geshtorbn ⟨shoyn⟩.

00:06:28.778 --> 00:06:30.571
BARUKH dayen emes.

00:06:30.803 --> 00:06:31.584
⟨a⟩ dank.

00:06:31.596 --> 00:06:33.378
un ikh mit mayn man...

00:06:35.983 --> 00:06:38.744
dos bin ikh mit mayn man mit di kinder,

00:06:39.038 --> 00:06:41.023
ven zey zenen nokh geven kleyn.

00:06:41.333 --> 00:06:43.402
geven a sheyne mishpokhe

00:06:43.408 --> 00:06:45.743
un ales, nor a kurts lebn.

00:06:46.378 --> 00:06:48.346
er iz yung geshtorbn,

00:06:48.403 --> 00:06:50.504
bay nayn un fertsik yor.

00:06:52.167 --> 00:06:55.812
dos iz gemakht gevoyrn, ge- in ⟨NOWO-⟩...?

00:06:54.512 --> 00:06:56.261
neyn, Tshernovits.

00:06:55.812 --> 00:06:56.863
in Tshernovits.

00:06:58.056 --> 00:07:01.085
ir hot demolts gevoynt a mol oykh in Tshernovits?

00:06:59.811 --> 00:07:05.589
Novoselits. neyn, neyn, undz ho'mir gevoynt in Novoselits, nor dos bild, gedenk ikh, ⟨iz⟩ in Tsherno⟨vits⟩.

00:07:01.085 --> 00:07:03.470
ale mol in ⟨NOWOSELITZA⟩?

00:07:05.589 --> 00:07:08.445
undz ze'mir geven in Tshernovits, ho'mir gemakht dos bild.

00:07:09.042 --> 00:07:13.373
er iz geven a kleyn yingele nokh, un zi iz shoyn gegan in ershtn klas.

00:07:14.307 --> 00:07:16.241
a dank, froy Lipis, a dank.

00:07:18.913 --> 00:07:21.239
do zenen di kinder shoyn groyse.

00:07:21.239 --> 00:07:23.034
zi hot shoyn gelernt

00:07:23.267 --> 00:07:24.765
in Moskve

00:07:24.765 --> 00:07:26.467
oyf tseyn-ARZT,

00:07:26.507 --> 00:07:31.445
un er hot gelernt in institut matematik groys.

00:07:31.907 --> 00:07:34.348
zenen zey gekumen aheym in gast,

00:07:34.472 --> 00:07:36.457
ze'mir oyf a khasene do.

00:07:36.582 --> 00:07:39.103
SNIMAET bay a khaver.

00:07:39.315 --> 00:07:41.030
ir mit ayer man.

00:07:40.446 --> 00:07:43.183
ikh mit mayn man mit zey beyde.

00:07:47.685 --> 00:07:53.129
dos iz mayn reyvekh. dos iz mayne eyniklekh tsvey, zoln zayn gezunt mit lange yor.

00:07:53.592 --> 00:07:56.160
itster nisht lang SNIMAET.

00:07:58.553 --> 00:08:01.601
vu iz dos gemakht gevorn, di fotografye?

00:08:00.375 --> 00:08:02.073
do in Berlin shoyn.

00:08:03.072 --> 00:08:04.206
yo.

00:08:04.071 --> 00:08:07.206
vi alt zenen di ey⟨UNK⟩?

00:08:05.657 --> 00:08:07.290
akhtsn yor.

00:08:07.290 --> 00:08:10.034
do ven zey zenen akhtsn yor gevorn.

00:08:12.694 --> 00:08:13.620
nu, ⟨s-⟩

00:08:13.620 --> 00:08:15.152
-pir az m'hot mikh...

00:08:17.031 --> 00:08:21.816
ven undz ho'mir gehert az m'hot umge- iber- dem arkhiv hot men gefunen

00:08:21.816 --> 00:08:23.080
in Vinitse,

00:08:23.080 --> 00:08:24.816
ze'mir geforn atin tsu tsu,

00:08:24.816 --> 00:08:28.367
⟨khotsh⟩ ikh hob ongeshribn. hot men mir geentfert mit dem papir

00:08:28.367 --> 00:08:31.724
az m'hot mikh getrofn in arkhiv dortn. ikh bin farshribn

00:08:31.724 --> 00:08:35.936
in MOGILЁV-Podolsk, denstmol ven undz ze'mir geven dortn oyf dem

00:08:35.936 --> 00:08:37.286
gutn plats.

00:08:37.286 --> 00:08:42.494
hobn zey getrofn mikh in di SPISKIs in arkhiv, hot men mir geshikt ot di spravke aheym.

00:08:43.677 --> 00:08:44.919
a dank.

00:08:44.676 --> 00:08:46.195
funem arkhiv.
